<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>New Chat Feature on Thriftify!</title>
  <style>
    .head-con {
      width: 100%;
      height: 40px;
      background-color: green;
      color: white;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }
    body {
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    section {
      padding: 20px;
    }
    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .cta {
      background-color: green;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="head-con">
      <h2 class="head">Thriftify</h2>
    </div>
  </header>
  <section>
    <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
    <p>
      We’ve just dropped a game-changing update on Thriftify — and we’re thrilled to tell you all about it!
    </p>
    <p>
      You can now <strong>chat directly with sellers and buyers</strong> right on the platform. Got a question about an item? Want to negotiate? Or just confirm something quickly? It's now super easy.
    </p>
    <p>
      Here’s what’s new:
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Real-time chat:</strong> Message sellers or buyers directly on Thriftify.</li>
        <li><strong>Last seen status:</strong> Know when someone was last online so you’re not left guessing.</li>
        <li><strong>Chat before you buy:</strong> Ask questions, confirm details, and build trust before making payment.</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
    <p>
      Whether you're looking to buy or sell, this new chat feature makes the experience faster, smoother, and more personal.
      Let's make buying and selling even more exciting!<br />
      <strong>The Thriftify Team</strong>
    </p>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
